<figureCitation box="[374,475,1877,1902]" captionStart="FIGURES 223–226" captionStartId="57.[151,264,1180,1202]" captionTargetBox="[154,1436,195,1158]" captionTargetId="figure@57.[151,1436,193,1159]" captionTargetPageId="57" captionText="FIGURES 223–226. Mesabolivar madalena sp. n. (223–224, ZFMK Ar 19071) and M. inmanis sp. n. (225–226, ZFMK Ar 19072). 223, 225. Epigyna, ventral views. 224, 226. Cleared female genitalia, dorsal views (arrow points at V-shaped sclerite). Scale lines:0.5." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1202575/files/figure.png" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">225–226</figureCitation>
