<figureCitation box="[486,585,1878,1902]" captionStart="FIGURES241–252" captionStartId="61.[151,264,1628,1650]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,193,1607]" captionTargetId="figure@61.[151,1436,193,1607]" captionTargetPageId="61" captionText="FIGURES241–252. Femaleepigyna in ventral views and cleared female genitalia in dorsal views, Mesabolivar togatus group (part2). 241–242.M.bico sp. n. (ZFMK Ar19065).243–244.M.mimoso sp. n. (ZFMK Ar 19069).245–246. M.madalenasp. n. (ZFMK Ar 19071). 247–248. M. inmanis sp. n. (ZFMK Ar 19072). 249. M. sp. (“sp. 7” in Astrin et al. 2006) (Br03/100- 14b). 250.M.cyaneomaculatus (Keyserling, 1891) (ZFMK Ar 19075). 251–252.M. claricae sp. n. (ZFMK Ar 19083)." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1202579/files/figure.png" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">247–248</figureCitation>
